en-US.summary: Find contact info for any Alexa team member.
en-US.name: team-lookup
en-US.description:
Find contact info for Alexa team members.

Alexa Team Lookup can find the person you want to find easily.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Alexa Team Lookup" or "Alexa, open Alexa Team Lookup" to start your search".

At any time, you can stop the search by saying "Alexa, stop"
